---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Shiiba Tatsuya | 名刺サイト</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center">
    <main class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg max-w-sm text-center">
      <img src="shiileaf01.jpg" alt="プロフィール画像" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4" />
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">Tatsuya Shiiba</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">インフラエンジニア / Cloud Engineer</p>

      <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mb-4">
        <a href="https://github.com/shlf6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <img src="icons8-github-100.png" alt="GitHub" class="w-6 h-6" />
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:contact@shiileaf.dev">
          <img src="icons8-mail-100.png" alt="Email" class="w-6 h-6" />
        </a>
        <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <img src="icons8-no-access-100.png" alt="X (旧Twitter)" class="w-6 h-6" />
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
        東京在住 / クラウド技術とIaCが得意です。<br />
        Let's build reliable systems together.
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
